Class DoublyLinkedList<T>

java.lang.Object
model.DoublyLinkedList<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of elements stored in the list.
All Implemented Interfaces:
Iterable<T>, Queue<T>, Stack<T>
public class DoublyLinkedList<T> extends Object implements Queue<T>, Stack<T>, Iterable<T>
A generic Doubly Linked List implementation that can be used as a Queue or a Stack.
